A RESOLUTION
1 Commending Carmen Smith, Sugar Hill Elementary School's 2024-2025 Teacher of the
2 Year; and for other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, Carmen Smith has been teaching second through fourth grade advanced content
4 math and enrichment math to Sugar Hill students at Sugar Hill Elementary School in
5 Gwinnett County for 18 years and has 29 years of teaching experience; and
6 WHEREAS, she is a highly respected second through fourth grade teacher within the school
7 community and among her peers and has been recognized as Sugar Hill Elementary School's
8 Teacher of the Year for 2024-2025; and
9 WHEREAS, she has spent endless hours both inside and outside the classroom teaching
10 students and empowering them to think freely, helping them develop skills such as
11 questioning, provoking, and challenging all the things presented to them; and
12 WHEREAS, she has engaged her students by producing innovative lessons that have real-life
13 applications and has thus promoted learning to her students as a lifelong endeavor; and
